{"title" : "户外拓展" ,"content":"<P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>户外拓展训练是模拟军事管理训练而衍生出来的一种培训项目，户外拓展培训是指利用自然地域（山川湖海）、通过模拟探险式情景结合为团队精心设计的拓展设施，达成解决或促进团队执行力、协作、领导力等</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><?xml:namespace prefix = 'o' ns = 'urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office' /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>企业户外拓展从根本上，需要满足企业需求，拓展精神与方式要与企业整体的发展及团队规划相一致。金牌拓展团队建立于人力资源管理从业经验基础之上，所以可根据企业需求，进行设计拓展培训项目。让每一个拓展项目都真正起到促进企业团队培训目标的作用。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 30pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 2.5'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>金牌户外拓展与众合作伙伴共同为企业推出四种类型户外拓展场地：</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 72pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -72pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -6.0'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>1<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、山地拓展：在高山之上，设置拓展设施、营房、碉堡、</SPAN>CS<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>，同时让员工在天然氧吧中，感受大山的巍峨。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 72pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -72pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -6.0'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>2<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、海滩拓展：在大海之畔，设置拓展设施、营房、沙滩休闲设施，同时让员工在大海的涛声中，感受大海的情怀。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 72pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -72pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -6.0'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>3<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、军营拓展：在部队培训基地，设置拓展设施、营房、拉练穿越等，同时让员工感受军营的严谨风气与军人崇高的奉献精神。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 72pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -72pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -6.0'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>4<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、运动拓展：在铺有绿荫的塑胶运动场，进行一场别开生面的拓展活动或趣味运动会，无需远足即可感受团队协作的快乐。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><B style='mso-bidi-font-weight: normal'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'><SPAN style='mso-spacerun: yes'>&nbsp; </SPAN><SPAN lang=ZH-CN>附</SPAN>1<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>： 户外拓展的优势：</SPAN></SPAN></B><B style='mso-bidi-font-weight: normal'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></B></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23.7pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -17.7pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -1.47; mso-para-margin-left: .57gd'><B><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>1<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>企业拓展训练以培养战无不胜的精英团队为宗旨</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>增强员工的心理抗压力</SPAN>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>让员工真实地面对心灵的脆弱和团队问题</SPAN>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>可使团队成员间感受亲密合作的成就与快乐，从而延伸至企业实际工作当中</SPAN>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>激发无限潜能</SPAN>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>铸造精英团队</SPAN>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23.6pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -17.7pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -1.47; mso-para-margin-left: .56gd'><B><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>2<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>户外团队拓展高度互动、实用新颖</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>场景寓意深刻</SPAN>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>发人深省</SPAN>.<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>使受训学员念念不忘</SPAN>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>是世界上培养个人潜能与团队精神最具创意的方式</SPAN>.<o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 29.45pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -17.7pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -1.47; mso-para-margin-left: 1.12gd'><B><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>3<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>针对企业效益低下、人才流失、跳槽等让企业头疼不己的问题，在通过参加企业团队户外拓展训练</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>人才流失率明显下降，团队合作精神和企业凝聚力大大加强。</SPAN><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23.55pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -11.8pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -.98; mso-para-margin-left: 1.12gd'><B><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>4<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>、</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>户外团队拓展训练分为场地拓展和纯野外拓展，两者结合对团队合作精神的要求非常高</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312'>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>使团队成员深刻认识到</SPAN>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>每个人的成长离不开团队</SPAN>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>每个人的成功都需要团队的鼓励与支持</SPAN>.<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>只有亲身体验过生命危机时刻</SPAN>,<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>才更加珍惜同伴的帮助。</SPAN><A name=2></A><A name=sub2311813_2></A><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23.5pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: -11.75pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: -.98; mso-para-margin-left: 1.12gd'><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 17.7pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-char-indent-count: 1.47'><B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>附</SPAN></B><B><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>2<SPAN lang=ZH-CN>：户外拓展训练五步环节</SPAN></SPAN></B><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>第一步：</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>体验</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23.95pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-left: 2.28gd'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>此乃过程的开端。参加者投入一项活动，并以观察、表达和行动的形式进行。这种初始的体验是整个过程的基础。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>第二步：</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>交流</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23.95pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-left: 2.28gd'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>有了体验以后，很重要的就是，参加者要与其它体验过或观察过相同活动的人交流他们的感受或观察结果。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>第三步：</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>分享</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23.95pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-left: 2.28gd'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>分享个人的感受，与其它人参加探讨、交流以及反映自己的内在生活模式。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>第四步：</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>整合</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23.95pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-left: 2.28gd'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>从经历中总结出原则并归纳提取出精华，以帮助参加者进一步定义和认清体验中得出结论。</SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; TEXT-INDENT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly'><B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>第五步：</SPAN></B><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>应用 </SPAN><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P><P class=MsoNormal style='BACKGROUND: white; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt 23.95pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 24pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-para-margin-left: 2.28gd'><SPAN lang=ZH-CN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'>策划如何将这些体验应用在工作及生活中。而应用本身也成为一种体验，有了新的体验，循环又开始了。</SPAN><A name=ref_[1]_2311813></A><SPAN style='FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; mso-hansi-font-family: Arial; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial'><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>"}